    "yg_info_CT6wLn": {
      "type": "yg-info",
      "settings": {
        "title": "About our best-selling electric bike collection",
        "richtext": "<p>The <strong>best electric bikes</strong> from Qlife are here! Here, we have carefully selected a range of premium electric bikes, including commuter e-bikes, fat tire e-bikes, folding e-bikes and trikes. Whether you need a reliable city commuter or an adventurous option for nature trails and mountains, we have the perfect choice for everyone.</p><h3><strong>Convenient and Versatile Electric Bike Transportation</strong></h3><p><strong>Great value for money: Electric bikes</strong> are a great way to cut down on transportation expenses, especially with fuel prices rising. In addition to saving money on fuel, the <strong>most affordable e-bikes</strong> also have lower maintenance and repair costs than cars.</p><p><strong>Convenient and flexible: </strong><a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/commuter-ebike\">Commuter e-bikes</a> make city transportation a breeze, allowing you to easily cut through congestion. For those seeking adventure, our fat tire e-bikes can handle a variety of terrains, from sand to mud and snow, adding a touch of excitement to your trip.</p><p><strong>Riding modes:</strong> Each Qlife electric bike comes with three riding modes: pure electric, pedal assist and regular riding. Switch between modes according to your needs and enjoy a customized riding experience.</p><p><strong>Stylish Design and Comfort</strong>: Our best electric bikes are carefully designed to balance performance and style, ensuring you travel in comfort and style.</p><h3><strong>How to Choose an Electric Bike?</strong></h3><p>When buying an electric bike, you can consider many aspects such as purpose, budget, range, motor type, battery capacity and frame style. Qlife offers a variety of electric bikes to suit different styles and functions, including:<br/>                ● <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/commuter-ebike\"><strong>Commuter Electric Bike</strong></a><strong>: </strong>Cityone 2.0 is our best-selling electric bike with a top speed of 28 mph and a range of up to 55 miles, perfect for city riding.<br/>                ● <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/fat-tire-electric-bike\"><strong>Fat Tire Electric Bike</strong></a><strong>:</strong> Models such as Racer Plus and Racer Fat Tire feature wide tires for stable and enjoyable riding on any terrain and in all weather conditions.<br/>                ● <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/folding\"><strong>Folding Electric Bike</strong></a><strong>: </strong>The lightweight Mars model is easy to store and transport, perfect for users who are often on the go.<br/>                ● <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/products/triker-folding-3-wheels-electric-bike\"><strong>Trike</strong></a><strong>:</strong> Our trikes are designed for stability and balance, suitable for riders of all ages and skill levels.</p><h3><strong>Why Choose Qlife?</strong></h3><p><strong>Value of Excellent Service:</strong> Qlife bikes guarantee quality at an affordable price, providing excellent value for your investment. If you have any questions or need help, our customer service team is here to help.</p><p><strong>Easy to Assemble and Use:</strong> Most of our electric bikes are 95% pre-assembled and can be on the road with a simple installation. Each bike includes detailed instructions and video tutorials to get beginners up and running quickly.</p><p>By choosing an Qlife electric bike, you not only get an enhanced riding experience, but also a stylish and practical means of transportation at an unbeatable price. Whether you are a beginner or an experienced rider, our team is eager to help you find the electric bike that best suits your needs and make riding an enjoyable part of your life!</p><p>By browsing our best-selling models today, start your eco-friendly journey!</p><p>Explore more high-quality electric bikes on Qlife: <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/fat-tire-electric-bike\" title=\"fat tire ebike\">fat tire ebike</a> | <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/folding\" title=\"Folding Electric Bikes\">folding electric bikes</a> | <a href=\"https://actbestbike.com/collections/commuter-ebike\" title=\"Commuter electric bikes\">commuter electric bikes</a></p>",
        "heading": "",
